normalize<-function(x) {
    sapply(x, function(y) {if(all(is.na(y))) {y}
           else if(sum(!is.na(y))!=1) {helper<- (y-min(y, na.rm=TRUE))/(max(y, na.rm=TRUE)-min(y, na.rm=TRUE)) 
                                      helper}
           else if(sum(!is.na(y))==1) {helper<-ifelse(is.na(y),0,1)
                 helper}
    })
}
